file.name: OpenApi_defn_with_array_in_form.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:@@@PORT@@@/PetStore
paths:
  /pet:
    post:
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/Pet'
      responses:
        '204':
          description: Empty Response.
components:
  requestBodies:
    Pet:
      content:
        application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              somearray:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: number
